						| &nbsp;&#8729;&nbsp;
						a href='support/index.html' Support
						| &nbsp;&#8729;&nbsp;
						a href='support/index.html#contact' Contact
					
				  p.mb-0.text-muted Designed by <a href='/' class='text-muted'>Adam Overholtzer</a> in California.
